Box 2558, Shallotte, NC 28459 Office Hours are 8:30 a.m. to 5:30 p.m., Monday through Friday, 31986=Copyright © 2015 The Brunswick Beacon is your source for local news, sports, events and information in Brunswick County, North Carolina and surrounding areas., 19038=The first of two kids fishing tournaments for the summer took place June 27 at the Brunswick County Fishing Club at Sunset Harbor and 11 kids participated. Prizes of fishing tackle and rod and reel outfits were awarded for the first and second largest fish and for the largest overall catch in the 8-and-under age group and the 9-12 age group. In addition, prizes were awarded for the ugliest fish caught and the best pictures of fish drawn.  }
